services.name: Pankaj Bhadouria
services.desc: Pankaj Bhadouria won the debut season of MasterChef India, which ran from October 16 to December 25, 2010, and Jayanandan Bhaskar ended as the runner-up of the show. She later hosted cooking shows like Chef Pankaj Ka Zayka, Kifayati Kitchen, 3 Course with Pankaj, etc.  The 51-year-old is the first MasterChef Winner worldwide to have an official MasterChef Cookbook in her name. Also, she has written two more cookery books “Barbie- I am a Chef” and “Chicken for My Kitchen”.

services.name: Shipra Khanna
services.desc: Shipra Khanna is among the popular MasterChef India winners. She has won people’s hearts not only by her cooking skills but also by her beauty and charisma. Khanna is the winner of the seance season of MasterChef India, which started airing on October 22, 2021 on Star Plus. That season of the show declared Salma Shazia Fatima as its runner-up.  In September 2013, she opened her first Restaurant in Gujarat’s Ahmedabad named “H.O.T.- House of Taste ” and in 2013, she opened her restaurant in New Delhi which is named “The Darzi Bar & Kitchen”.  The followers-count on Instagram is not less than that of any Bollywood actress. Over 4.5 million people follow the beautiful MasterChef on Instagram.

services.name: Ripudaman Handa
services.desc: The third season of MasterChef India was won by Ripudaman Handa and After winning the show, he received many offers from the other shows. He also participated as a contestant in Nach Baliye Season 6 and hosted the TV show Junior MasterChef Swaad Ke Ustaad. Along with that he also hosted Bhojpuri cooking show Roj Hoyi Bhoj.

services.name: Customize Food
services.desc: You can select from a list of options to build your own dish, such as adding or removing specific vegetables, sauces, cheeses, or meats on a pizza or salad.

services.name: Korean
services.desc: Korean cuisine is a vibrant symphony of flavors and textures, centered around fluffy white rice and a diverse array of side dishes called banchan. The most famous of these, kimchi, features fermented vegetables like cabbage and radish seasoned with chili flakes, garlic, and ginger. Korean meals often highlight fresh seafood, marinated meats like bulgogi, and savory stews like sundubu jjigae

services.name: Italian
services.desc: Italian cuisine, known for its simplicity and fresh ingredients, boasts a variety of regional specialities. From the iconic pasta dishes like creamy carbonara or hearty lasagna, to the wood-fired pizzas loaded with mozzarella and basil, Italian food emphasizes quality ingredients and bold flavors. Fresh seafood, vibrant vegetables, and regional cheeses like parmesan and gorgonzola all play a key role, while robust olive oil and fragrant herbs add depth to every bite. Don't forget the sweet finale-- from rich tiramisu to refreshing gelato, Italian food offers a delectable journey from savory to sweet.
